            <p><strong>Aadhar no {!contact.Aadhar_Card_Number__c}</strong> (hereinafter called as Employee), Joining Quadrobay Technologies as <strong>{!contact.Designation__c}</strong> on dated (in the format- Date/Month/ Year) <strong>{!contact.Hire_Date__c}</strong></p>
