            <p>Data Misuse is not acceptable. In any event, a significant breach of Data might lead to other legal severe consequences and subject to a penalty of Minimum of Three-Month Salary with job termination without notice and the company will not issue any work experience certificate and officially put on record.</p>

            <h2>IN WITNESS WHEREOF</h2>
            <p>The Parties hereto agree to the terms of this Agreement and signed on the dates written below.</p>

